title: NERI/AU, Contours of dispersion of volcanic ash over Europe, Europe, 2010
name: NERI/AU, Contours of dispersion of volcanic ash over Europe, Europe, 2010
description: Test contour was generated by grabbing the frame from the 120 hr simulation of dispersal of ash plume. Then it was georeferenced and turned into a raster, which was then filtered to remove small values. Contours were generated from the resulting raster.

author.source: The AARHUS universities National Environmental Research Institute website
